title: Scrapheap Challenge - 11x03 - Water Power.avi
description:
"Dicks Diamonds" line-up includes regulars Dick Strawbridge and Jim Milner along with guest team member Steve Matthews.

Dick's challengers are "The Rocketeers", "South Devon Scholars" and "The Young Ones"

The challenge : to construct a water-powered vehicle.

Please help me seed & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them.
